1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,880
<b>The Moment Everything Started</b>

2
00:00:02,880 --> 00:00:07,050
I still remember the first time I saw you.

3
00:00:07,050 --> 00:00:12,114
Maybe it was just another normal day for the world.

4
00:00:12,114 --> 00:00:13,206
But for me…

5
00:00:13,206 --> 00:00:16,682
It became the day my story changed.

6
00:00:16,682 --> 00:00:18,966
You walked into my life

7
00:00:18,966 --> 00:00:22,739
And suddenly everything felt brighter.
